title: Brandan Schieppati from Rise Above Fitness/Bleeding Through
itunes:title: Brandan Schieppati from Rise Above Fitness/Bleeding Through
description:
On this episode I have a very introspective conversation with frontman for Bleeding Through, Brandan Schieppati. He now owns a gym in Huntington Beach, CA called Rise Above Fitness and one afternoon I made my way to his gym for an in depth discussion about depression, the desire for control and intensity. Please donate to the show!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
